%%{init: {'flowchart': {'compactMode': true}}}%%

sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor PM as Program Manager
participant UI as Legal UI
participant BFF as Legal BFF
participant CACHE as Redis Cache
participant SERVICE as Legal Validation Service
participant READDB@{ "type": "database", "alias": "EPMS schema"}

PM ->> UI: Open Legal Landing Page
UI ->> BFF: getLegalRequestList(filters)

BFF ->> CACHE: Check legal request list cache
alt Cache Hit
    CACHE -->> BFF: Cached request list
else Cache Miss
    BFF ->> SERVICE: fetchLegalRequestList(userId, filters)
    SERVICE ->> READDB: GET legal requests by user/role/status
    READDB -->> SERVICE: Approved/Open/Sent Back list
    SERVICE -->> BFF: Request list
    BFF ->> CACHE: Cache request list
end

BFF -->> UI: Show Legal request list with status

PM ->> UI: Click request number
UI ->> BFF: getLegalRequestDetail(requestId)
BFF ->> SERVICE: fetchRequestDetail(requestId)
SERVICE ->> READDB: GET request, document metadata, comments, decision history
READDB -->> SERVICE: Request detail
SERVICE -->> BFF: Detail response
BFF -->> UI: Show request details and comments history